I've never thought I would come back here with you.

696
00:52:26,685 --> 00:52:29,965
Why? Didn't you have any hope for us?

697
00:52:29,965 --> 00:52:31,685
How could I dare to hope for it?

698
00:52:31,685 --> 00:52:34,775
There was barely any possibility.

699
00:52:34,775 --> 00:52:36,360
How could you say that?

700
00:52:36,360 --> 00:52:38,460
I was sending you all kinds of signals since we were living at my house.

701
00:52:38,460 --> 00:52:41,910
But you were always acting cool.

702
00:52:41,910 --> 00:52:44,350
So you had been flirting with me all those times?

703
00:52:44,350 --> 00:52:46,260
You are quite daring.

704
00:52:46,260 --> 00:52:47,970
That's right.

705
00:52:47,970 --> 00:52:50,270
Because you were acting cool.

706
00:52:50,270 --> 00:52:55,255
We almost died before we got together.

707
00:52:55,255 --> 00:52:58,520
Even though we almost died, I think it's worth it.

708
00:52:58,520 --> 00:53:02,090
Sitting here on the beach.

709
00:53:02,090 --> 00:53:03,960
Holding your hand like this.

710
00:53:03,960 --> 00:53:07,000
No matter how much blood I lost, I don't regret it.

711
00:53:13,330 --> 00:53:17,385
Anyway, I still want you to follow your dream.

712
00:53:17,385 --> 00:53:22,230
You told me that you want to go and study music abroad.

713
00:53:22,230 --> 00:53:24,880
I want you to pursue it.

714
00:53:24,880 --> 00:53:27,570
No matter how much I want to be with you,

715
00:53:27,570 --> 00:53:30,315
I don't want you to give up on your dream.

716
00:53:30,315 --> 00:53:32,515
What about us?

717
00:53:33,280 --> 00:53:35,683
You don't need to worry about us.

718
00:53:35,683 --> 00:53:38,000
I'll be right here waiting for you.

719
00:53:38,000 --> 00:53:40,755
Even though we will get
to see each other only once a year,

720
00:53:40,755 --> 00:53:44,015
I'll wait for you here, on our beach.

721
00:53:44,995 --> 00:53:48,975
Next year, I'll come back to see the hostel's owner.

722
00:53:48,975 --> 00:53:50,535
Sure.

723
00:53:50,535 --> 00:53:52,670
I'll prove to you...

724
00:53:52,670 --> 00:53:58,630
that a boy from a fisherman village
who only knows about fishing can take care of you.

725
00:53:58,630 --> 00:54:02,470
Do you still hold a grudge against me?

726
00:54:05,760 --> 00:54:08,600
You don't need to prove anything anymore.

727
00:54:09,990 --> 00:54:15,045
I know that you are the one
who loves and cherishes me the most.

728
00:54:16,885 --> 00:54:20,390
I want you to live the life that you want.

729
00:54:26,675 --> 00:54:31,610
The life that I want is the life
that I can be with you.

730
00:54:49,050 --> 00:54:50,740
Can I ask something from you?

731
00:54:50,740 --> 00:54:51,885
What is it?

732
00:54:51,885 --> 00:54:53,980
Stop calling me Mr. Nueng.

733
00:54:53,980 --> 00:54:55,425
Just call me Nueng.

734
00:54:55,425 --> 00:54:56,365
Alright, Nueng.

735
00:54:56,365 --> 00:54:58,995
Also stop talking politely to me. No couples do that.

736
00:54:58,995 --> 00:55:00,675
Sure, Nueng.

737
00:55:00,675 --> 00:55:05,065
From now on, you are no longer my boss.

738
00:55:05,065 --> 00:55:09,390
But you are the one and only love of my life.

